evidence.text:
We select those tasks that involve PII information. Specifically,
for each action step per task, we use both GPT-4 (Achiam et al., 2023) and GPT-4o (OpenAI, 2024)
to determine whether PII is involved and to identify the PII category.

Mitigations include, but are not limited to:

●  dataset ﬁltering;
●  conditional pre-training;
●  supervised ﬁne-tuning;
●
●  safety policies and desiderata;
●  product-level mitigations such as safety ﬁltering.
